<Page x:Class="Hardcodet.Wpf.Samples.Help.Sleep"
	xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
	xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
	Title="Sleep" 
	>
    <FlowDocumentReader ViewingMode="Scroll">
        <FlowDocument FontSize="20">
            <Paragraph>
                <Image Source="/Images/help1.png" Width="190" Height="190" Margin="0,0,30,0" />
                <Run FontSize="30" BaselineAlignment="Center">Sleep</Run>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold FontSize="24">Examples:</Bold>
            </Paragraph>
            <List>
                <ListItem>
                    <Paragraph>
                        <Bold>Sleep</Bold>
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Table CellSpacing="5" BorderThickness="1" BorderBrush="Black">
                        <TableRowGroup>
                            <TableRow>
                                <TableCell>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Image Source="/Images/PrimitivesSleep.PNG"  Margin="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalAlignment="Center" />
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </TableCell>
                            </TableRow>
                        </TableRowGroup>
                    </Table>

                    <Table CellSpacing="5" BorderThickness="1" BorderBrush="Black">
                        <TableRowGroup>
                            <TableRow>
                                <TableCell>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Image Source="/Images/LogicSleep.PNG"  Margin="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalAlignment="Center" />
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </TableCell>
                            </TableRow>
                        </TableRowGroup>
                    </Table>

                    <Paragraph>
                        <Italic>Explanation of example</Italic> - Sleep allows your script to pause for the number of milliseconds specified in the value of Entity1. In the example the script will wait for 1 second before executing the next statement.
                        <LineBreak/>
                    </Paragraph>
                </ListItem>


            </List>
            <Paragraph>
                <Line Stretch="Fill" Stroke="Black" X2="1"/>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold FontSize="24">Columns:</Bold>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>Sleep</Bold> - Sleep allows your script to pause for the number of milliseconds specified in the value of Entity1. Here are the columns:
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        1. Sequence
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Sequence is a decimal number with 4 digits after the decimal. It can be modified to allow you to insert rows anywhere in your script. Rows are executed in sequence number order.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        2. Verb
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Sleep
            </Paragraph>


            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        3. Entity1
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Entity1 is the name of a primitive that has been defined in the primitives tab. The value of the Entity1 is the number of milliseconds that you want the script to wait before continuing to the next statement.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        4. Relationship
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Relationship is not used.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        5. Entity2
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Entity2 is not used.
            </Paragraph>





        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentReader>
</Page>
